@startuml petri_net_3_aircraft_deadlock_fixed
title **Petri Net Model: Aircraft Turnaround Process — Deadlock-Free**\n**3 Aircraft + GSE Permit Control Place (Deadlock Fix)**

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam ranksep 30
skinparam nodesep 15

' ============================================================
' STYLES
' ============================================================
skinparam usecase {
    BackgroundColor<<state>> #FFFFFF
    BorderColor<<state>> #444444

    BackgroundColor<<resource>> #FFF3CD
    BorderColor<<resource>> #CC8800

    BackgroundColor<<initial>> #D4EDDA
    BorderColor<<initial>> #228B22

    BackgroundColor<<done>> #D6E9FF
    BorderColor<<done>> #3366CC

    BackgroundColor<<final>> #FFD700
    BorderColor<<final>> #B8860B

    BackgroundColor<<control>> #C8E6C9
    BorderColor<<control>> #2E7D32
}

skinparam rectangle {
    BackgroundColor<<t>> #444444
    FontColor<<t>> white
    BorderColor<<t>> #222222

    BackgroundColor<<fork>> #1A5276
    FontColor<<fork>> white

    BackgroundColor<<join>> #1A5276
    FontColor<<join>> white

    BackgroundColor<<safety>> #922B21
    FontColor<<safety>> white
}

' ============================================================
' SHARED RESOURCES
' ============================================================

usecase "**Runway**\n**Available**\n(1 token)" as RWY <<initial>>
usecase "**Gate/Bay**\n**Available**\n(1 token)" as BAY <<initial>>
usecase "**Fuel Truck**\n**Available**\n(1 token)" as FUEL <<resource>>
usecase "**Catering Truck**\n**Available**\n(1 token)" as CAT_R <<resource>>
usecase "**Cleaning Team**\n**Available**\n(1 token)" as CLN_R <<resource>>
usecase "**Baggage Cart**\n**Available**\n(1 token)" as BAG_R <<resource>>
usecase "**Apron Zone**\n**Slots Available**\n(2 tokens)" as APRON <<resource>>

usecase "**GSE Permit**\n**(Control Place)**\n**[2 tokens]**" as PERMIT <<control>>

' ============================================================
' ARRIVAL (Shared by all 3 aircraft)
' ============================================================

usecase "**3 Aircraft**\n**Waiting to Land**\n(3 tokens)" as WAIT <<initial>>

rectangle "Land on\nRunway" as T_LAND <<t>>
usecase "Aircraft\non Runway" as ON_RWY <<state>>
rectangle "Taxi to\nGate" as T_TAXI <<t>>
usecase "Aircraft\nTaxiing" as TAXIING <<state>>
rectangle "Dock at Gate\n(Chocks + GPU)" as T_DOCK <<t>>
usecase "Aircraft\nDocked" as DOCKED <<state>>
rectangle "Passengers\nDisembark" as T_DEBARK <<t>>
usecase "All Passengers\nOff Aircraft" as PAX_OFF <<state>>

WAIT --> T_LAND
RWY --> T_LAND : "acquire\nrunway"
T_LAND --> ON_RWY
ON_RWY --> T_TAXI
T_TAXI --> TAXIING
T_TAXI --> RWY : "release\nrunway"
TAXIING --> T_DOCK
BAY --> T_DOCK : "acquire\ngate"
T_DOCK --> DOCKED
DOCKED --> T_DEBARK
T_DEBARK --> PAX_OFF

note right of T_LAND
  Runway มี 1 token
  เครื่องลงจอดทีละลำ
  A1 -> A2 -> A3
end note

note right of T_DOCK
  Bay มี 1 token
  จอดได้ทีละลำ
  ลำก่อนต้อง Pushback
  ออกก่อน
end note

' ============================================================
' FORK: Parallel Ground Handling
' ============================================================

rectangle "Start Ground\nHandling\n(FORK)" as T_FORK <<fork>>
PAX_OFF --> T_FORK

usecase "Waiting for\nRefueling" as W_FUEL <<state>>
usecase "Waiting for\nCatering" as W_CAT <<state>>
usecase "Waiting for\nCleaning" as W_CLN <<state>>
usecase "Waiting for\nBaggage\nHandling" as W_BAG <<state>>
usecase "Waiting for\nMaintenance\nInspection" as W_MNT <<state>>

T_FORK --> W_FUEL
T_FORK --> W_CAT
T_FORK --> W_CLN
T_FORK --> W_BAG
T_FORK --> W_MNT

' ============================================================
' BRANCH 1: REFUELING (needs Fuel + Apron + Permit)
' ============================================================

rectangle "Start\nRefueling" as T_S_FUEL <<safety>>
usecase "Refueling\nin Progress" as REFUELING <<state>>
rectangle "Finish\nRefueling" as T_E_FUEL <<t>>
usecase "Refueling\nComplete" as FUEL_DONE <<done>>

W_FUEL --> T_S_FUEL
FUEL --> T_S_FUEL : "acquire\nfuel truck"
APRON --> T_S_FUEL : "acquire\napron slot"
PERMIT --> T_S_FUEL : "**acquire**\n**GSE permit**"
T_S_FUEL --> REFUELING

REFUELING --> T_E_FUEL
T_E_FUEL --> FUEL_DONE
T_E_FUEL --> FUEL : "release\nfuel truck"
T_E_FUEL --> APRON : "release\napron slot"
T_E_FUEL --> PERMIT : "**release**\n**GSE permit**"

' ============================================================
' BRANCH 2: CATERING (needs Catering + Apron + Permit)
' ============================================================

rectangle "Start\nCatering" as T_S_CAT <<t>>
usecase "Catering\nin Progress" as CATERING <<state>>
rectangle "Finish\nCatering" as T_E_CAT <<t>>
usecase "Catering\nComplete" as CAT_DONE <<done>>

W_CAT --> T_S_CAT
CAT_R --> T_S_CAT : "acquire\ncatering truck"
APRON --> T_S_CAT : "acquire\napron slot"
PERMIT --> T_S_CAT : "**acquire**\n**GSE permit**"
T_S_CAT --> CATERING

CATERING --> T_E_CAT
T_E_CAT --> CAT_DONE
T_E_CAT --> CAT_R : "release\ncatering truck"
T_E_CAT --> APRON : "release\napron slot"
T_E_CAT --> PERMIT : "**release**\n**GSE permit**"

' ============================================================
' BRANCH 3: CLEANING (needs Cleaning only — inside cabin)
' ============================================================

rectangle "Start Cabin\nCleaning" as T_S_CLN <<t>>
usecase "Cabin Cleaning\nin Progress" as CLEANING <<state>>
rectangle "Finish Cabin\nCleaning" as T_E_CLN <<t>>
usecase "Cabin Cleaning\nComplete" as CLN_DONE <<done>>

W_CLN --> T_S_CLN
CLN_R --> T_S_CLN : "acquire\ncleaning team"
T_S_CLN --> CLEANING

CLEANING --> T_E_CLN
T_E_CLN --> CLN_DONE
T_E_CLN --> CLN_R : "release\ncleaning team"

' ============================================================
' BRANCH 4: BAGGAGE (needs Baggage + Apron + Permit)
' ============================================================

rectangle "Start Baggage\nHandling" as T_S_BAG <<t>>
usecase "Baggage\nHandling\nin Progress" as BAGGAGE <<state>>
rectangle "Finish Baggage\nHandling" as T_E_BAG <<t>>
usecase "Baggage\nHandling\nComplete" as BAG_DONE <<done>>

W_BAG --> T_S_BAG
BAG_R --> T_S_BAG : "acquire\nbaggage cart"
APRON --> T_S_BAG : "acquire\napron slot"
PERMIT --> T_S_BAG : "**acquire**\n**GSE permit**"
T_S_BAG --> BAGGAGE

BAGGAGE --> T_E_BAG
T_E_BAG --> BAG_DONE
T_E_BAG --> BAG_R : "release\nbaggage cart"
T_E_BAG --> APRON : "release\napron slot"
T_E_BAG --> PERMIT : "**release**\n**GSE permit**"

' ============================================================
' BRANCH 5: MAINTENANCE (no resource needed)
' ============================================================

rectangle "Start Transit\nMaintenance" as T_S_MNT <<t>>
usecase "Maintenance\nInspection\nin Progress" as MAINT <<state>>
rectangle "Finish Transit\nMaintenance" as T_E_MNT <<t>>
usecase "Maintenance\nInspection\nComplete" as MNT_DONE <<done>>

W_MNT --> T_S_MNT
T_S_MNT --> MAINT
MAINT --> T_E_MNT
T_E_MNT --> MNT_DONE

' ============================================================
' JOIN: All 5 branches must complete
' ============================================================

rectangle "All Ground\nHandling Done\n(JOIN)" as T_JOIN <<join>>
usecase "Ground Handling\nAll Complete" as GH_DONE <<done>>

FUEL_DONE --> T_JOIN
CAT_DONE --> T_JOIN
CLN_DONE --> T_JOIN
BAG_DONE --> T_JOIN
MNT_DONE --> T_JOIN
T_JOIN --> GH_DONE

' ============================================================
' PHASE 3: DEPARTURE
' ============================================================

rectangle "Calculate\nWeight & Balance" as T_WB <<t>>
usecase "Loadsheet\nApproved by\nCaptain" as WB_OK <<state>>

GH_DONE --> T_WB
T_WB --> WB_OK

rectangle "Passengers\nBoard Aircraft" as T_BOARD <<t>>
usecase "All Passengers\nBoarded\nDoors Closed" as BOARDED <<state>>

WB_OK --> T_BOARD
T_BOARD --> BOARDED

rectangle "Pushback\nfrom Gate" as T_PUSH <<safety>>
usecase "Aircraft\nPushed Back\nEngine Started" as PUSHED <<state>>

BOARDED --> T_PUSH
T_PUSH --> PUSHED
T_PUSH --> BAY : "release gate\n(A2 can dock now)"

rectangle "Takeoff" as T_TAKEOFF <<t>>
usecase "**Aircraft**\n**Departed**" as DEPARTED <<final>>

PUSHED --> T_TAKEOFF
RWY --> T_TAKEOFF : "acquire\nrunway"
T_TAKEOFF --> DEPARTED
T_TAKEOFF --> RWY : "release\nrunway"

' ============================================================
' NOTES: HOW GSE PERMIT PREVENTS DEADLOCK
' ============================================================

note top of PERMIT #E8F5E9
  <size:14>**GSE Permit — Control Place (Deadlock Fix)**</size>

  **tokens = 2** (เท่ากับ Apron Zone capacity)

  **หลักการ:**
  ทุก GSE ที่ต้องใช้ Apron Zone
  (Fuel, Catering, Baggage)
  ต้อง acquire GSE Permit ด้วย

  ถ้า Permit หมด -> GSE ตัวถัดไปรอ
  จน GSE ตัวก่อนเสร็จ แล้วคืน Permit

  **ผลลัพธ์:** ไม่มีทางที่ GSE > 2 ตัว
  จะเข้า Apron พร้อมกัน
  -> **ไม่เกิด Circular Wait**
  -> **ไม่เกิด Deadlock**
end note

note bottom of DEPARTED #E8F5E9
  <size:14>**Execution Trace (Deadlock-Free)**</size>

  **=== Aircraft 1 (A1) ===**
  | Step | Event | Permit | Apron |
  | 1 | A1: Start Refueling | 2->**1** | 2->**1** |
  | 2 | A1: Start Catering | 1->**0** | 1->**0** |
  | 3 | A1: Start Baggage -> **WAIT** | 0 (รอ) | 0 (รอ) |
  |   | (Cleaning + Maint ทำได้เลย ไม่ใช้ Apron/Permit) | | |
  | 4 | A1: Finish Refueling | 0->**1** | 0->**1** |
  | 5 | A1: Start Baggage -> **OK!** | 1->**0** | 1->**0** |
  | 6 | A1: Finish Catering | 0->**1** | 0->**1** |
  | 7 | A1: Finish Baggage | 1->**2** | 1->**2** |
  | 8 | A1: JOIN fires (5/5 done) | | |
  | 9 | A1: W&B -> Board -> Pushback | | release Bay |
  | 10 | A1: Takeoff -> **Departed** | | |

  **=== Aircraft 2 (A2) ===**
  | 11 | A2: Land -> Taxi -> Dock (Bay ว่างแล้ว) | | |
  | 12 | A2: Debark -> FORK -> ทำ GH เหมือน A1 | | |
  | ... | (ซ้ำเหมือน A1 โดยไม่มี deadlock) | | |
  | 20 | A2: Takeoff -> **Departed** | | |

  **=== Aircraft 3 (A3) ===**
  | 21-30 | ซ้ำเหมือน A1, A2 | | |
  | 30 | A3: Takeoff -> **Departed** | | |

  ----
  **Final Marking: P_Departed = 3 tokens**
  **ทรัพยากรทั้งหมดคืนสู่ค่าเริ่มต้น**
end note

note right of T_FORK
  **FORK (1 -> 5):**
  แยก 5 branches
  ทำพร้อมกัน

  **Cleaning** + **Maintenance**
  เริ่มได้เลยไม่ต้องรอ
  เพราะไม่ใช้ Apron/Permit
end note

note right of T_JOIN
  **JOIN (5 -> 1):**
  ต้องครบ 5 branches:
  Refuel Done
  + Catering Done
  + Cleaning Done
  + Baggage Done
  + Maintenance Done
end note

note left of T_S_FUEL #FFF3CD
  **ต้อง acquire 3 อย่าง:**
  1. Fuel Truck (1 token)
  2. Apron Slot (จาก 2 tokens)
  3. GSE Permit (จาก 2 tokens)
end note

note left of T_PUSH #FFEBEE
  **Safety Constraint:**
  Pushback ได้ก็ต่อเมื่อ
  Refueling Complete แล้ว
  (JOIN บังคับอยู่แล้ว)
end note

note right of CLEANING
  **ไม่ใช้ Apron / Permit**
  ทำงานในห้องโดยสาร
  -> เริ่มได้เลยทันที
end note

note right of MAINT
  **ไม่ใช้ Apron / Permit**
  วิศวกรเดินตรวจรอบเครื่อง
  -> เริ่มได้เลยทันที
end note

' ============================================================
' INITIAL MARKING SUMMARY
' ============================================================

note top of WAIT
  <size:14>**INITIAL MARKING (M0)**</size>

  |= Place |= Tokens |
  | Aircraft Waiting to Land | **3** |
  | Runway Available | **1** |
  | Gate/Bay Available | **1** |
  | Fuel Truck Available | **1** |
  | Catering Truck Available | **1** |
  | Cleaning Team Available | **1** |
  | Baggage Cart Available | **1** |
  | Apron Zone Slots | **2** |
  | **GSE Permit (Control)** | **2** |
  | All other places | **0** |

  ----
  **Petri Net Summary:**
  Places = 22 per aircraft + 9 resources
  Transitions = 20 per aircraft
  3 aircraft share same net structure
  with common resource places
end note

@enduml
